/svg></span></button></div></div></div><p><strong>Full Changelog</strong>: <a href="https://github.com/brandmooffin/cocos2d-mono/compare/2.4.4...2.4.5" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://github.com/brandmooffin/cocos2d-mono/compare/2.4.4...2.4.5</a></p><p>NuGet Packages:</p><p><a href="https://www.nuget.org/packages/Cocos2D-Mono.Android/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Cocos2D-Mono.Android</a>
